diagrams.mermaid:
flowchart TD
  Start([新診斷子宮內膜癌]) --> MolTest{4 分子分群<br>POLE + MMR + p53 IHC}

  MolTest -->|POLEmut| POLE[POLEmut track:<br>預後極佳<br>可考慮降階治療]
  MolTest -->|MMRd/MSI-H| MMRd[MMRd track:<br>IO 高度敏感<br>Lynch screen]
  MolTest -->|p53abn| p53[p53abn track:<br>預後最差<br>升階 + HER2 testing]
  MolTest -->|NSMP| NSMP[NSMP 標準路徑]

  POLE --> Stage1{Stage?}
  MMRd --> Stage1
  p53 --> Stage1
  NSMP --> Stage1

  Stage1 --> S_IA[IA1/IA2 endometrioid<br>低風險]
  Stage1 --> S_IB[IB low-grade]
  Stage1 --> S_IC[IC aggressive histology]
  Stage1 --> S_II[Stage II]
  Stage1 --> S_III[Stage III]
  Stage1 --> S_IV[Stage IV]

  S_IA --> Fertility{保留生育?}
  Fertility -->|是 + grade 1| FS[Fertility-sparing<br>Progestin therapy<br>3-6 月 D&C 追蹤]
  Fertility -->|否| SurgIA[TAH + BSO ± SLN<br>POLEmut: 可 observation<br>其他: adjuvant brachy 視 HIR]

  S_IB --> SurgIB[TAH + BSO + SLN/LND<br>+ vault brachy<br>PORTEC-2 standard]

  S_IC --> SurgIC[完整 staging<br>+ adjuvant chemo<br>HER2+: + Trastuzumab]

  S_II --> SurgII[TAH + BSO + LND<br>+ adjuvant pelvic RT<br>p53abn: + chemo]

  S_III --> SurgIII[Staging surgery<br>+ adjuvant chemo + RT<br>PORTEC-3 standard<br>NRG-GY018 / RUBY 加 IO]

  S_IV --> Sys[Systemic therapy<br>Pac/Carbo + Pembro NRG-GY018<br>或 + Dostarlimab RUBY<br>HER2+: + Trastuzumab]

  classDef pole fill:#d4edda,stroke:#27ae60,stroke-width:2px;
  class POLE pole;
  classDef mmrd fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#c89a3a,stroke-width:2px;
  class MMRd mmrd;
  classDef p53 fill:#f8d7da,stroke:#c0392b,stroke-width:2px;
  class p53 p53;
  classDef nsmp fill:#e8f0e0,stroke:#5a7a4a;
  class NSMP nsmp;
  classDef sysclass fill:#f0e8ff,stroke:#7a5aa8;
  class Sys,FS sysclass;

flowchart TD
  Surgery([TAH + BSO 術後病理]) --> Mol{分子分群}

  Mol -->|POLEmut + stage I-II| POLE_low[**Observation**<br>PORTEC-4a 等試驗支持]

  Mol -->|p53abn 任何 stage| p53_high[**升階治療**:<br>Adjuvant chemo + RT<br>不論 anatomic stage]

  Mol -->|MMRd / NSMP| Risk{解剖風險分群}

  Risk -->|Low risk<br>IA G1-2 no LVSI| LowRisk[Observation]

  Risk -->|HIR<br>GOG-99 criteria| HIR[**Vaginal brachy**<br>PORTEC-2 證實 = pelvic RT]

  Risk -->|High risk<br>IB G3 / II-III / serous| HighRisk[**CCRT + adjuvant chemo**<br>PORTEC-3 standard<br>OS HR 0.70]

  Risk -->|Stage III dMMR| Pembro_adj[考慮 Pembro 加 adjuvant<br>但 KEYNOTE-B21 negative<br>NCCN 列為選項]

  classDef low fill:#d4edda,stroke:#27ae60;
  class POLE_low,LowRisk low;
  classDef med fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#c89a3a;
  class HIR med;
  classDef high fill:#f8d7da,stroke:#c0392b;
  class p53_high,HighRisk,Pembro_adj high;

flowchart TD
  Start([Advanced/recurrent endometrial cancer]) --> MMR{MMR / MSI status}

  MMR -->|dMMR / MSI-H| L1_dMMR[第一線首選:<br>Dostarlimab + Pac/Carbo RUBY<br>OR Pembro + Pac/Carbo NRG-GY018<br>**dMMR PFS HR 0.28-0.30**]

  MMR -->|pMMR / MSS| L1_pMMR[第一線:<br>Pembro + Pac/Carbo<br>OR Durva + Pac/Carbo + Olap DUO-E<br>OR Pac/Carbo ± Bev]

  L1_dMMR -->|progression| L2_dMMR[後線:<br>Pembrolizumab 單藥<br>或 Dostarlimab 單藥]

  L1_pMMR -->|progression| L2_pMMR[後線:<br>**Lenvatinib + Pembrolizumab**<br>KEYNOTE-775<br>OS 17.4 vs 12.0 月]

  L2_dMMR -->|progression| Salvage[後線 salvage:<br>Docetaxel/Carbo<br>Doxorubicin/Cis<br>Hormone therapy ER/PR+]
  L2_pMMR -->|progression| Salvage

  Salvage --> HER2{HER2 status}
  HER2 -->|HER2+ serous/CS| Tras[Trastuzumab 加組合<br>或 Trastuzumab deruxtecan]
  HER2 -->|HER2-| Hormone[Hormone therapy:<br>MPA / Megestrol<br>± Tamoxifen 交替]

  classDef dmmr fill:#d4edda,stroke:#27ae60;
  class L1_dMMR,L2_dMMR dmmr;
  classDef pmmr fill:#fff3cd,stroke:#c89a3a;
  class L1_pMMR,L2_pMMR pmmr;
  classDef her2 fill:#f0e8ff,stroke:#7a5aa8;
  class Tras her2;
